OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLittle change, further rain at
OL,6,Ftimes in the west and north, becoming
OL,7,Fmore widespread and heavy in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Drier in the east with a
OL,9,Flittle brightness at times in the
OL,10,Fmorning. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will stay cloudy through
OL,13,Fthe evening and overnight with further
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain, heavy at times.
OL,15,FWindy at times, especially towards
OL,16,Fmorning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
