OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FSome bright spells possible
OL,6,Fin east at first. Otherwise cloudy and
OL,7,Fwindy with rain, heavy and persistent
OL,8,Fat times. Clear spells and blustery
OL,9,Fshowers in the evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,12,Fon Friday and Saturday with bright
OL,13,Fspells and a few showers, these mainly
OL,14,Fin the west. Further rain expected
OL,15,Flater Saturday. Cloudy and windier on
OL,16,FSunday with further rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
